## Known Patterns & Gotchas
- Vercel `env pull` shows AGENT_INTERNAL_TOKEN as empty (encrypted) ‚Äî use VPS .env directly
- Middleware blocks non-internal paths even if route handler has Bearer auth ‚Äî must add to `isAssistantWorkerBypassPath()` in `src/lib/agent-internal-auth.ts`
- Local `next build` exits 1 due to missing DATABASE_URL ‚Äî expected, Vercel has it
- PWA service worker can cache stale builds ‚Äî users may need hard refresh after deploy

